name: PhysicianonFIRE
0:
”Alexa, start Physician on FIRE”
”Read the latest blog post”
”Find blog posts about Retirement”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: physician on fire
des:
Physician on FIRE is a collection of personal finance blog posts created to inform and inspire both physicians and our patients with insightful writing from a physician who has attained financial independence and the ability to retire early.

NOTE: If you have an Amazon Fire TV Stick, you may need to use the alternate Physician on FIRE skill called P. O. F. If you enable both skills, "Physician on FIRE" and "P. O. F." you can get the same great content using both invocations "Alexa, start Physician on FIRE" and "Alexa, start P. O. F."

You can find out more about the Physician on FIRE blog at www.PhysicianOnFire.com.

Engage the skill by saying:
Alexa, Start Physician on FIRE

Once the skill is engaged, try the following commands:
Play the latest podcast
Search for posts on Financial Independence
Tell me about Physician on FIRE
Help


**For information about this Alexa skill, visit www.CreateMyVoice.com or send an email to Support@CreateMyVoice.com
